<plot>A short film about the fall of the Berlin Wall and the German Unification of 1989-90. Both events are documented through carefully selected shots. The film includes genuine footage about people lining up to visit the western side a week after the Mauerfall. It also documents the overall feeling briefly after the unification.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?065701</url></doc>
